Welcome to use the services provided by Butter Camera! Muke Company (referred to in this privacy agreement as Beijing Muke Technology Co., Ltd., hereinafter also referred to as "we") attaches great importance to the protection of your privacy and personal information. This privacy agreement applies to your access and use of the services provided by Butter Camera through any means.
Butter Camera is a product for beautification and interactive communication of pictures and videos. You can use Butter Camera to achieve personalized editing services for pictures or videos (hereinafter collectively referred to as "Butter Camera products or services"). We will only process the personal information necessary for you to use our products or services.
This privacy agreement applies to the software development kits (SDK) and application programming interfaces (APIs) you use through Butter Camera’s web and mobile terminals (including but not limited to Apps and mini-programs), for third-party websites and applications. and other ways to access and use our products and services.
Butter Camera includes but is not limited to multiple application versions such as iOS and Android. When using Butter Camera, please choose the version that matches the installed terminal device. The personal information that Butter Camera may obtain depends on the version of the Butter Camera application you are using, the specific type/version of the terminal device you are using, and the functions you are using.
This privacy agreement is designed to help you understand what personal information we collect, why we collect it, what we do with it and how we protect it. We will collect and use your personal information in accordance with the Privacy Agreement, but will not collect all of your personal information in a mandatory manner just because you authorize and agree to this Privacy Agreement.
We will strictly comply with legal and regulatory requirements and obtain your separate consent in specific circumstances. In addition to this privacy agreement, we may also explain to you our rules for processing your personal information through product page notifications, pop-up prompts, information push, etc. The processing of personal information corresponding to specific business functions will be subject to specific rules. , the specific rules have the same effect as this Privacy Agreement.
Unless otherwise provided by laws and administrative regulations, you have the right to know and decide how we process your personal information, and you have the right to restrict or refuse us or other parties from processing your personal information; at the same time, you have the right to request We explain the personal information processing rules we provide to you. Please read and understand this privacy agreement carefully before using Butter Camera and related products and services in order to make appropriate choices.
