1. Information we collect and corresponding purposes of use
We will collect and use your personal information in accordance with the principles of lawfulness, legitimacy and necessity. Specifically,
we collect and process your personal information in order to provide you with corresponding business functions.
In the corresponding function, if you provide other people's personal information, please ensure that you have obtained authorization from the relevant subject. We reserve the right to verify the legal source of such personal information at any time.
You need to provide us with personal information for us to implement basic business functions of registration and login (mobile phone number login and third-party platform login, etc.), purchase and payment of physical goods. The information necessary to realize basic business functions is necessary personal information. If you refuse to provide these necessary personal information, we will not be able to provide you with the basic business functions and corresponding services.
In addition to basic business functions, you may choose to provide us with some personal information for us to implement expanded business functions such as publishing, participating in operational activities, and customer service processing. We will inform you of the purpose of use and process this personal information based on your authorization or the purposes necessary to achieve the expanded business functions you choose. Your refusal to provide such extended business function information will not affect your use of our basic business functions. However, if you refuse to provide the personal information necessary to realize the extended business functions, we will not be able to provide you with the extended business functions.
To facilitate your understanding, the business functions we provide, the purposes of processing and the personal information required are listed below:
1.1. Register and log in to your account
If you use the functions or services provided by Butter Camera, such as taking pictures or filming, editing pictures or videos, publishing, etc., you need to register and log in to a Butter Camera account. You can create a Butter Camera account through your mobile phone number or email, and you can complete your account information.
When registering and logging in to a Butter Camera account, you need to provide us with your mobile phone number. You can choose to set the account name, avatar, login password, and account binding email address.
You can also use a third-party account (such as WeChat, Weibo, QQ, Facebook) to log in to Butter Camera. At this time, you will authorize Butter Camera to obtain the public information you registered in the third-party account (including your nickname, avatar and other information authorized by you).
You can choose whether to log in to Butter Camera through the "one-click login" method. If you choose this login method, the operator will process your mobile phone number information.
1.2. Publishing and interaction
When you publish pictures or video content, we will collect the video or picture content you upload as well as text content such as titles, and display your nickname, avatar, published content and other information.
When you share information or receive shared information, we will read the passwords, links and other content in the clipboard to jump and share the information content.
When you follow or share an account, or browse, collect, follow, comment, like, and forward, we will collect your aforementioned information and display the content published by the account of the corresponding content publisher.
In principle, the information you choose to publish publicly will be visible to all users. If it involves your personal information or even sensitive personal information, please consider it carefully. If the information you publish publicly involves other people's personal information, you must obtain their consent before disclosing it.
1.3. Filming and Recording
Butter Camera provides you with shooting and recording functions.
If you use the shooting and recording function service, we will apply for the camera, microphone and storage (or album) permissions of your device system. With your authorization and consent, you can use the shooting and recording functions.
You can learn more about the photo or recording function services through "Home Page - Editing - Shooting or Recording" in Butter Camera.
You can obtain your camera, microphone, storage (or photo album) permissions by canceling the system authorization at any time. Afterwards, you may not be able to use the above-mentioned related services or functions, or be unable to achieve the intended purpose of the above-mentioned related functions and services. effect, but it will not affect your normal use of other business functions of Butter Camera that are not based on the above permissions.
1.4. Image or video editing
Butter Camera provides you with picture or video editing functions.
If you use editing functions or services, we will apply for storage (or photo album) permissions on your device system. With your authorization and consent, you can store your edited pictures or video content.
You can learn more about editing function services through "Home Page - Editing" in Butter Camera.
You can at any time cancel the system authorization for Butter Camera to obtain your storage (or photo album) and stop our collection of your information. After that, you may not be able to use the above-mentioned related services or functions, or be unable to achieve the above-mentioned related functions. The effect intended to be achieved by the service will not affect your normal use of other business functions that are not based on the above permissions.
1.5. Intelligent (one-click) beauty treatment
Butter Camera provides you with automatic face-based beautification function.
If you use the smart (one-click) beauty service, we will only collect and process your facial information locally to complete the smart (one-click) beauty function or service.
You can learn more about the
intelligent (one-click) beauty service through "Edit-Portrait-One-click Beauty" in Butter Camera.
Our processing of your facial information is only completed locally and is only used for this function, and unless otherwise explicitly stated and with your consent, we will not return, store or share any of your facial feature value information.
