Butter Camera will launch operational activities for newly launched services and functions from time to time. If the launch of a new service requires processing your personal information or applying for device system permissions without your prior authorization and consent, we will obtain your consent separately, among which , if the processing of sensitive personal information is involved, we will obtain your separate consent.
